Outside of [[an hero|crossing the River Stix]] there is currently no treatment for HPD. Drugs don't help and group therapy only gives them another platform to show off their [[unwarranted self importance|extremely interesting and unique personalities]]. Due to this unfortunate circumstance they continue to infest the [[tube]]s and clog them with their beautiful selves.

